"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Blockchain cybersecurity company CertiK has raised $80 million in a Series B2 funding round led by Sequoia Capital China that pushed its valuation to nearly $1 billion, [the company announced in a blog post](https://www.certik.io/resources/blog/announcements/CertiK-Closes-$80M-Investment-Round#home). The round marks CertiK’s third round of funding within four months, with total investments coming in at just above $140 million.\\n\\nOther participating investors included Tiger Global, Coatue Management and GL Ventures, a venture capital arm of Hillhouse Capital.\\n\\nThe company’s active monitoring platform Skynet detects and protects blockchains from cyberattacks. CertiK also offers the Security Leaderboard, a security ranking platform for blockchain protocols and decentralized finance (DeFi) projects.\\n\\n“CertiK is on a mission to globally secure the crypto world of blockchains and smart contracts. CertiK has already demonstrated this through tremendous growth of its business, and support of security audits for a large volume of over 1800 clients so far,” said CertiK in its blog post.\\n\\nCertiK says its revenue has grown by 20 times over the past year. The company has quadrupled its headcount over that period. CertiK recently hired Dr. David Tarditi, a veteran of engineering and research teams at Microsoft, to serve as engineering vice president.\\n\\nBlockchain security companies have become popular among venture capital investments. Investments have increased more than ten times over the past year to surpass $1 billion, according to [Crunchbase data](https://news.crunchbase.com/news/crypto-security-startups-vc-investment/) from August. Security and compliance startup Fireblocks [contributed $310 million](https://www.coindesk.com/business/2021/07/27/crypto-custody-firm-fireblocks-raises-310m-at-2b-valuation/) of the total after its fundraise in July.\\n\\n***Read More: [Blockchain Security Firm CertiK Raises $24M in Funding Round](https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2021/08/17/blockchain-security-firm-certik-raises-24m-in-funding-round/)***\",\"timestamp\":1638370060,\"title\":\"Blockchain Security Firm CertiK Raises $80M at Nearly $1B Valuation\"},\"digest\":\"rWvUFf6ZFlcb_ea9Dl4Himh7zglnuwiN_BjargnrJGw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x59C9d046d43B28816393825a3688D93B82bdd625\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RfdW5GkTlRq4QBZZRdKRwpCc_yxlSNT1LoA8_5Tva0g\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"UOESWGATHnPp5QcVFYCsicRsEhukO00kD8caSSuRhKY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"xhkEpot1ti-27YVlNRRWPBqeo5LrFYM5PkBzby_qjlQxApqfJTCfQqOVqYfuWpH3qp6R5NmX6eVNDYId9wt1Kg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x759994437ec6810c5427799d94968db7aedc5343608f9fe19450186699f323322fb5f6548c4cda2d952dfd6861ce14980d099f50015aceaa96e685ad9d9e9fdd1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RfdW5GkTlRq4QBZZRdKRwpCc_yxlSNT1LoA8_5Tva0g\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"UOESWGATHnPp5QcVFYCsicRsEhukO00kD8caSSuRhKY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"rWvUFf6ZFlcb_ea9Dl4Himh7zglnuwiN_BjargnrJGw\"}"